			<p class="mb-0"> TopMovies is one of the best sources for movies, designed to help fans explore the world of movies  and decide what to watch.</p>
			<ul class="text-center">
				<li> <span>We can help you find a movie to your liking based on the genres you like.</span></li>
				<li><span>We have a rating system that lets users vote for the rating of a movie.</span></li>
				<li><span>You can see all the actors that were in the movie including the roles they played</span></li>
			</ul>
