			<h1 id="why-register">Why should I register on TopMovies?</h1>
			<p class="mb-0"> Registering on IMDb opens up the ability to enjoy the following features:</p>
			<ul class="text-center">
				<li><span>Rate movies.</span></li>
				<li><span>Make a review of a movie.</span></li>
				<li><span>Add a movie to your watched movies list.</span></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center">
			<h1 id="how-to-rate">How do I submit my rating?</h1>
			<p class="mb-0"> Any registered TopMovies user can easily rate any TopMovies title. Rating titles is a great way to share your opinion and keep track of what you've seen</p>
			<p>To submit your rating, navigate to the title page and you'll see the average user rating will show at the top of the screen with yellow stars.</p>
			<p>Click the star to the right and select the number of stars to save your rating!</p>
			<p>Our ratings are on a scale from 1 - 10. 1 meaning the title was terrible and one of the worst titles you've seen and 10 meaning you think it was excellent.</p>
		</div>
